{"tid":1423414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國眾議院 議長：香港示威者表現出極大勇氣  激動人心","createTime":"2019-08-06T13:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T16:53:28.000Z","uid":227801,"like":285,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"7d169b12cf94ec77b4589f23bea0792b5055e75d","tid":1423414,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:50:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=358185&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D358185%26refer%3D&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2Bv%2FGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=7a4ec5ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D358185%26refer%3D&h=2f3472d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=358185&amp;refer=</a><br />\n【Now新聞台】美國眾議院議長佩洛西發表聲明，支持香港「反送中」示威者，兩黨議員將在國會復會後，推動香港人權與民主法案。<br />\n<br />\n佩洛西說入夏以來，香港人一直向全世界發出一個激動人心的訊息，就是自由、正義和民主的理想，永不會被威嚇和不公義澆滅。<br />\n<br />\n她又說香港人表現出極大勇氣，跟拒絕尊重法治、不願履行一國兩制義務的懦弱政府，形成極其鮮明的對比，香港立法會應立即徹底、並永久撤銷逃犯條例修訂工作。<br />\n<br />\n她指民主共和兩黨的國會議員將在九月，國會休會期結束後，開始推動香港人權與民主法案，為保香港民主自由和法治奮鬥。<br />\n<br />\n外交部駐港特派員公署強烈譴責佩洛西公然支持暴力抗法分子，粗暴干預香港事務和中國內政，中方對此表示強烈不滿和堅決反對。"},{"pid":"7570add9bc131d5e191480165f7ace6f076dc20d","tid":1423414,"uid":25601,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:53:42.000Z","msg":"過左未個人權法"},{"pid":"450a0dbeda002899d4426aff94e43faed333fce3","tid":1423414,"uid":181649,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"7570add9bc131d5e191480165f7ace6f076dc20d","tid":1423414,"uid":25601,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:53:42.000Z","msg":"過左未個人權法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:55:20.000Z","msg":"Congress放緊假點過"},{"pid":"ab806876dc2450ddb6d7b2ff7213a5591d91f059","tid":1423414,"uid":51840,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"7570add9bc131d5e191480165f7ace6f076dc20d","tid":1423414,"uid":25601,"lik